{"tid":435861,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"2017-18 LIHKG香港女神總會盃第一圈投選專區(171015)","createTime":"2017-10-14T15:59:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-15T17:58:22.000Z","uid":92376,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"65047e4e9cfc893f122294d72fe14e243cd37749","tid":435861,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T15:59:47.000Z","msg":"以下為即將舉行之賽事<br />\n會員可留意稍後時間發出的比賽專用回覆並以回覆評分功能進行投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(唔識點樣用回覆評分功能黎投票既巴打可以參考下面既教學)<br />\n<br />\n由首場12:10am開始,每兩分鐘開賽一場<br />\n<br />\n(冠)莊錠欣v周慧敏(乙)<br />\n(甲)譚嘉儀(模)v游蕙禎(甲)<br />\n(非)楊文蔚v方皓玟(非)<br />\n(乙)湯洛雯v彭慧中(冠)<br />\n(乙)陳婉婷v袁澧林(冠)<br />\n(冠)孫慧雪v李幸倪(非)<br />\n(乙)駱文捷v菊梓喬(乙)<br />\n(乙)何雁詩v江嘉敏(非)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/hiNda68.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FhiNda68.png&h=d4221617&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/s2sfX8L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fs2sfX8L.png&h=b53ffa65&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b5744d388217420b6938c22254053240478fea00","tid":435861,"uid":92376,"like":31,"dislike":11,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T16:00:02.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2017-18 LIHKG香港女神總會盃第一圈</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">*括號內數字為聯賽排名(非聯賽者則以非聯表示)</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2017-10-15 12am-10pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/kXWjbxb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FkXWjbxb.png&h=88ea7795&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/HScnebc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FHScnebc.png&h=6e4838c4&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(冠15)莊錠欣vs周慧敏(乙10)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">盃賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">盃賽不設額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"9d96b3261d38ee632f39c0e852ddfc237d6e5437","tid":435861,"uid":92376,"like":21,"dislike":27,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T16:01:59.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2017-10-15 12:02am-10:02pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/aaV8PwE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FaaV8PwE.png&h=214a94d8&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/DiJ28Rh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FDiJ28Rh.png&h=b1165d16&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(甲11)譚嘉儀(模)vs游蕙禎(甲10)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">盃賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">盃賽不設額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"2ccd96c0b8cd3e577c4e417c58e502b71dfc5992","tid":435861,"uid":92376,"like":32,"dislike":9,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T16:04:19.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2017-10-15 12:04am-10:04pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/xpTrMBY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FxpTrMBY.png&h=cc22f35c&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/6hoYLMa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F6hoYLMa.png&h=0e515224&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(非聯)楊文蔚vs方皓玟(非聯)</div><br />\n<br /